* 0.6       02.10.2006  Christoph Winkelmann
- base on cpufrequtils
- drop temperature support
- SMP support

* 0.5.5     24.11.2005  Christoph Winkelmann
- bugfix: configuration was not loaded correctly (patch from Paul Cannon)

* 0.5.4     09.11.2005  Christoph Winkelmann
- remove degree sign for encoding incompatibilities
- display slider optionally

* 0.5.3     01.11.2005  Christoph Winkelmann
- fixed typo in target 'install-sudo' in Makefile
- change governor via new script for more flexibility (ondemand governor)
- check for ondemand governor when reading frequency

* 0.5.2     18.10.2004  Christoph Winkelmann
- cpufreqset does not assume order in scaling_available_frequencies

* 0.5.1     16.03.2004  Christoph Winkelmann
- scaling factor for temperature added

* 0.5       15.03.2004  Christoph Winkelmann
- update plugin once a second only
- display cpu temperature optionally
- display cpufreq governor optionally
- toggle governor when clicking on governor name
- optionally set userspace governor when moving slider
- reserve more height for text and slider
- added 'install-sudo' target to Makefile
- check for >1 cpu in cpufreqset

* 0.4       31.01.2004  Christoph Winkelmann
- make economic and efficient use of available interfaces

* 0.3.3     28.01.2004  Christoph Winkelmann
