* 0.3.2     12.01.2004  Christoph Winkelmann
- improved documentation
- improved Makefile

* 0.3.1     12.01.2004  Christoph Winkelmann
- always get cpu frequency from /proc/cpuinfo
- get khz_max with khz
- save khz_max in configuration
- hand over absolute frequency to cpufreqset

